cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CE, cs.SY 

This paper is about developing a method for predicting the performance of reinforcement learning and bandit algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the estimation of variance, which is related to statistics and data analysis (cs.DS). The application of the method to improve advertisement design suggests a connection to computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the mention of convergence rates and uncertainty quantification suggests a connection to control systems (cs.SY).
